  "subject": "Reimplement Terminate as asynchronous",
  "commit_message": "Reimplement Terminate as asynchronous\n\nWith the recent changes ot Rsync n terms of rsync registration,\nstatus query, appcontext status and others, DCM now has to\nasynchronously check when the appcontext status has become Terminated\nbefore finally claiming that a Logical Cloud is not applied and\nconsequently removing all respective appcontext etcd handles.\n\nIssue-ID: MULTICLOUD-1143\nChange-Id: I0ff166b3225124c8b647d8dc1cacb15b691a2f4c\nSigned-off-by: Igor D.C <igor.duarte.cardoso@intel.com>\n",
